{% extends "base.jinja" %}

{% block title %}Content{% endblock title %}

{% block header %}
<h1>Avali Content</h1>
{% endblock header %}

{% block content %}
<div class="content">
    <p>
        Sadly, Avali content is scattered to the four winds, lost in Discord servers,
        and ancient subreddit posts, lost to time. <br>
        This page attempts to fix that, by giving all avali content a centralised home.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <h2>3D/VR Avatars</h2>
    <div class="dock">
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Da'vali</h3>
            <p>The Da'vali model is only available in the Avali Army discord server</p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/avali">Get it! (Discord)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Kita'vali</h3>
            <p>
                Similar to the Da'Vali model, the Kita'vali model can only be downloaded from Discord.
                In this case, the Kita's Gremlinhouse server.
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/kitavali">Get it! (Discord)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Lorc'Avali</h3>
            <p>
                Yep, yet another discord-only download. This time through the LorcanVR's Avatars server.
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/vymTCmVMnw">Get it! (Discord)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Floofvali (paid)</h3>
            <p>
                Finally, breaking the trend from Discord-only downloads, we have the Floofvali, on Gumroad
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://jinxyuwu.gumroad.com/l/floofvali">Buy it! (Gumroad)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Paw'vali (paid)</h3>
            <p>
                A Kemono-style avali! Available on gumroad.
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://jinxyuwu.gumroad.com/l/floofvali">Buy it! (Gumroad)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Jerry Avali (paid)</h3>
            <p>
                Another popular model! Available on gumroad
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://wispweaver.gumroad.com/l/JerryAvali">Buy it! (Gumroad)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <h2>Stickers</h2>
    <div class="dock">
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Lostvali Stickers</h3>
            <p>
                Lost has a HUGE collection of stickers, all of them are on telegram, however,
                if you have Discord Nitro, you can use the Discord ones globally. There are
                so many stickers here, that they don't all fit into one telegram sticker pack
                So you'll need to add both packs to get the whole set.
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://telegram.me/addstickers/lostavali">Get pack 1! (Telegram)</a>
                </div>
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://telegram.me/addstickers/loststickervol2">Get pack 2! (Telegram)</a>
                </div>
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/B75FX9D8S5">Get (most of) them! (Discord)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Benevolence "Bee" Starmelody @ArisuStarfall Animated</h3>
            <p>
                Some really nice avali animated stickers here!
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://t.me/addstickers/Bee_Animated">Get them! (Telegram)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <h2>Avali Scratch Resources</h2>
    <div class="dock">
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>AnnoyingRains' sheets</h3>
            <p>
                AnnoyingRains (that's me!) has made a printable PDF with both sequenced alphabet and vocabulary drills
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="/static/content/AnnoyingRains/avali scratch practice.pdf">Get it! (Right here!)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Xyphurr's alphabet drills</h3>
            <p>
                Xyphurr has made a printable PDF with extensive sequenced alphabet drills
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://xyphurr.tplinkdns.com/nextcloud/s/bipckfQg3CRxcJ8">Get it! (Personal site)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Avali Scratch Font</h3>
            <p>
                SomeGuyNamedDavid made the main avali scratch font!
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://fontstruct.com/fontstructions/show/1108804/avali_scratch">Get it! (Fontstruct)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <h2>Games and Mods</h2>
    <div class="dock">
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Avali (Triage) Race Mod - Starbound</h3>
            <p>
                The continuation of RyuujinnZERO's original Avali race mod!
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=729558042">Get it! (Steam Workshop)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pod">
            <h3>Ammonia Snowdrift (unreleased)</h3>
            <p>
                Heavy WIP Unreleased open-world multiplayer RPG set on Avalon, home of the Avali! <br>
                The game appears to be based on the lore mentioned in <a href="/lore/book">Todd's book</a>. <br>
                The project seemingly only has one active developer, and is still a long way away
                from releasing fully.
            </p>
            <div class="dock">
                <div class="pod">
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/BKPkWmb">Learn about it! (Discord)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock content %}